    {
        "content": "<p>Very minor note: I have a shorter proof of the recently merged <a href=\"https://imperialcollegelondon.github.io/FLT/docs/FLT/Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/RestrictedProduct.html#Continuous.restrictedProduct_map\">Continuous.restrictedProduct_map</a> at <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/24915\">#24915</a> (arguably I didn't advertise it at all and I should have made a PR to FLT instead). The core of the argument is the same of course.</p>",
